        {
          "html": "<div style=\"--color-midnight-ink:#000000;--color-deep-graphite:#111111;--color-charcoal-surface:#191919;--color-dark-slate:#202020;--color-medium-gray:#3a3a3a;--color-stone-accent:#606060;--color-light-steel:#b4b4b4;--color-almost-white:#eeeeee;--color-highlight-orange:#DA5C2C;--font-berkeleymono:'IBM Plex Mono',monospace;--font-inter:'Inter',sans-serif;background:var(--color-midnight-ink);padding:40px 24px;width:600px;box-sizing:border-box;\"><p style=\"font-family:var(--font-berkeleymono);font-size:14px;line-height:1.57;color:var(--color-almost-white);font-weight:400;margin:0 0 32px 0;\">Empowering 30,000+ teams with accelerated insights.<br>From high-growth startups to global enterprises.</p><div style=\"display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:16px;\"><div style=\"background:var(--color-charcoal-surface);border:1px solid var(--color-medium-gray);border-radius:2px;overflow:hidden;\"><div style=\"padding:20px 20px 16px 20px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--color-medium-gray);\"><p style=\"font-family:var(--font-berkeleymono);font-size:10px;font-weight:400;color:var(--color-stone-accent);letter-spacing:0.08em;margin:0 0 12px 0;\">SAVINGS</p><div style=\"font-family:var(--font-berkeleymono);font-size:20px;font-weight:700;color:var(--color-almost-white);margin:0 0 12px 0;\">hapn</div><p style=\"font-family:var(--font-berkeleymono);font-size:12px;line-height:1.6;color:var(--color-light-steel);margin:0;font-weight:400;\">Axiom lets Hapn query a petabyte of AWS Lambda events to manage 4 billion messages.</p></div><div style=\"padding:20px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--color-medium-gray);\"><p style=\"font-family:var(--font-berkeleymono);font-size:12px;line-height:1.6;color:var(--color-almost-white);margin:0 0 16px 0;font-weight:400;\">&ldquo;We chose Axiom because it&rsquo;s the only product out there that allows me to affordably see all my logs for a year. And it&rsquo;s very good at that.&rdquo;</p><div style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;\"><div style=\"width:32px;height:32px;border-radius:9999px;background:var(--color-medium-gray);flex-shrink:0;\"></div><div><p style=\"font-family:var(--font-berkeleymono);font-size:11px;font-weight:700;color:var(--color-almost-white);margin:0;\">Andres Hernandez</p><p style=\"font-family:var(--font-berkeleymono);font-size:11px;color:var(--color-stone-accent);margin:2px 0 0 0;font-weight:400;\">Co-founder &amp; CTO, Hapn</p></div></div></div><div style=\"padding:14px 20px;\"><a href=\"#\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-berkeleymono);font-size:12px;color:var(--color-almost-white);text-decoration:underline;font-weight:400;\">Hapn case study →</a></div></div><div style=\"background:var(--color-charcoal-surface);border:1px solid var(--color-medium-gray);border-radius:2px;overflow:hidden;\"><div style=\"padding:20px 20px 16px 20px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--color-medium-gray);\"><p style=\"font-family:var(--font-berkeleymono);font-size:10px;font-weight:400;color:var(--color-stone-accent);letter-spacing:0.08em;margin:0 0 12px 0;\">SIMPLICITY</p><div style=\"font-family:var(--font-berkeleymono);font-size:20px;font-weight:700;color:var(--color-almost-white);margin:0 0 12px 0;\">Cal.com</div><p style=\"font-family:var(--font-berkeleymono);font-size:12px;line-height:1.6;color:var(--color-light-steel);margin:0;font-weight:400;\">Switching to Axiom, Cal.com engineers solve customer problems easier and more reliably.</p></div><div style=\"padding:20px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--color-medium-gray);\"><p style=\"font-family:var(--font-berkeleymono);font-size:12px;line-height:1.6;color:var(--color-almost-white);margin:0 0 16px 0;font-weight:400;\">&ldquo;The beautiful thing about Axiom is it just works. No complications, no rubbish. It&rsquo;s way quicker to find that one thing you want to do.&rdquo;</p><div style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;\"><div style=\"width:32px;height:32px;border-radius:9999px;background:var(--color-medium-gray);flex-shrink:0;\"></div><div><p style=\"font-family:var(--font-berkeleymono);font-size:11px;font-weight:700;color:var(--color-almost-white);margin:0;\">Bailey Pumfleet</p><p style=\"font-family:var(--font-berkeleymono);font-size:11px;color:var(--color-stone-accent);margin:2px 0 0 0;font-weight:400;\">Co-founder &amp; CEO, Cal.com</p></div></div></div><div style=\"padding:14px 20px;\"><a href=\"#\" style=\"font-family:var(--font-berkeleymono);font-size:12px;color:var(--color-almost-white);text-decoration:underline;font-weight:400;\">Cal.com case study →</a></div></div></div></div>",
